reviewText: I have not heard from him yet but when I do i WILL LET YOU KNOW IF THERE IS A NEED FOR MORE INFORMATION.

Good demo for the Garmin Rino.
I was a basic user of GPS.
Since I got this I am now able to get so much more out it.
Highly recommended!

Very general coverage of the capabilities of this great gps.
Not very good production, low budget. Better than the manual.
Would have been a good buy for $12.99, but not worth what they are
charging.
